unnormalised: yeunarya parishade vixim, tumi nond gheumchi ki abstract submit korpachi nimani tarik 15/07/2024 meren vaddoileya. organizing committee 22/07/2024 meren sweekrutichi suchnau pattoita. parishad 05/08/2024 thaun 07/08/2024 meren, dar disa sokallim 9:00 vazta thaun sanjechim 5:00 vazta meren asa. delegates-ank vinanti asa ki timnni aapli hajri 29/07/2024 meren nischit korchi je vorvim logistical vevostha, jevnnachea ani boskochye vevosthechi nimani vevostha zaunk xokta. tumchem swagat korunk ami utsuk asat.
normalised: yeuupi conference vishayant, krupa korun nod geunche ki abstract patthovpachi antim tarik pandhra July don hazar chovis meren vaddoileli asa. organizing committee bayis July don hazar chovis meren manyata suchna dhaddpachi asha korta. conference panch August don hazar chovis thaun saat August don hazar chovis meren, dar disa nau A-M thaun panch P-M meren tharavleli asa. delegate-ank krupa korun apli hajri unnis July don hazar chovis meren pakki korchi vinanti asa jeathaun logistical vevastha, jevnnasakat, ani boskechim vevastha nimanni korunk yeta. ami tumchem svagat korpak utsuk asat.
